Description:
UNDER OFFER/ UNDER CONTRACT
Cranbourne East: If you are looking for a great home with all of the creature comforts then this home is yours for the taking! This sensational floorplan oozes comfort and class from the minute your walk in the front door allowing you the opportunity to literally unpack and relax!
The floorplan features 4 genuine robed bedrooms on offer plus study nook. The master bedroom is complete with walk-in robe and full ensuite with dual vanities. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 are all nicely distributed throughout the top floor & in a good proximity to the family bathroom.
If you are a firm believer that the kitchen is where the heart of the home is then you won't be disappointed. Complete with all of the mod cons there are stone bench tops, plenty of cupboard space plus quality stainless steel appliances including a 900mm cook top and oven & dishwasher, bench to ceiling tile splashback and walk in pantry complete with power. All this overlooking the great size kitchen meals area with sliding door access to the back yard.
Added extras include, ducted heating, two split system air conditioners, powder room downstairs, neutral tones, quality floor coverings throughout including carpets and floorboards and to top it off solar hot water.
Step outside and enjoy the decked pergola area, perfect for entertaining all year round with the folding café panels with memory plastic that makes it user friendly with kids and pets. The low maintenance landscaping means little upkeep but with room for the kids and pets to have a little run about.
The great street scape immediately ads to the overall appeal and includes a 2 car garage with internal access and porched entry just to top it off.
Sensational location nearby to family parkland and established shopping facilities together. Sport and recreation facilities & public transport are all close by. There is also easy access to both Fountain Gate and the Cranbourne Park shopping centre, whist you can take full advantage of the immediate freeway access if you happen to work in the CBD!

Description:
IS THIS THE BEST BUY FIRST HOME IN CRANBOURNE EAST?
This 3 year old home is amazing value and perfect for the first home buyers, savvy investors or the stylish downsizers. No compromises here!
Finished to level rarely seen, this clever floorplan is immaculately presented throughout. A tasteful combination of neutral tones with flooring including quality ceramics, floating timber boards and carpets. The home is sun drenched front to back with an abundance of windows furnished with quality Holland blinds (including blockout).
The home is well zoned ensuring privacy and space. It offers a clever, functional and attractive floorplan with accommodation including: generous sized master bedroom with WIR and ensuite while the remaining bedrooms have BIRs and utilise the large central bathroom with separate toilet. A wide long hallway with skylight leads to the rear of the home where the functional floorplan story begins.
An initial builders adaption sees the 3rd bedroom able to be opened up through double cavity sliding doors to add additional space to the living room as required. The 3rd bedroom has its own private mini courtyard.
The large light filled living, dining areas and kitchen offers views of the private landscaped yard. The kitchen includes Smeg oven, cooktop and dishwasher, an abundance of cupboards, walk in pantry and ample bench space.
Complete with just enough stylish landscaping front and back, fully fenced, Crim Safe door security camera's front and back, remote door garage (large) with storage cupboard and internal access to the home, covered al fresco (servery from Kitchen) with roll down café blinds, ducted heating, split system cooling and ceiling fans. The laundry is spacious with external access.
There is a sense of peace, privacy and security and this home exudes quality throughout and demands your attention.
Located in the much sought after Parksedge Estate, close to natural parks, lakes and playgrounds as well as Casey Race and the Indoor Sports Centre, childcare centres, shopping centres, many schools and public transport (most only 5 minutes away). Dont forget the planned Cranbourne East train Station.
Be quick to inspect this one!

Description:
listedAS - TITLED & CORNER 510M2 Block Ready to Build on EAST!
WELCOME TO EAST This block is titled and ready to go if you are!
Located in East Estate, EAST is an established community in the heart of Cranbourne East. One of Melbourne's most rapidly evolving suburbs. The nearby suburbs of Cranbourne and Berwick offer everything from major supermarkets, providores, cafes, restaurants and specialty retail stores. Cranbourne Park shopping centre is on your doorstep and Westfield Fountain Gate, the second largest shopping centre in Australia, is just a short car drive away.
With surrounding parklands and reserves, it offers a relaxed country feel, only to be complemented by already established homes in a new vibrant neighbourhood. Enjoy the conveniences of Cranbourne CBD, the Train Station, excellent sporting and aquatic facilities; Casey Complex and Casey RACE all a few minutes away, while South Gippsland Highway provides easy access to other major arterials.
This Corner Block is relatively flat and ready to build on.
The block measures at approx. 510m2 and is ready for you to build your ideal starter home or investment property.
To view the documentation &/or for further details, please call

Description:
The One You Don't Want to Miss
Located within the highly sought-after Mayfield Estate this beautifully presented stylish low maintenance family home will not be available for long!
OFFERS CLOSE SATURDAY 31ST AUGUST *unless sold prior.
Featuring four generous bedrooms each comprise a built-in robe, whilst the master suite offers a full ensuite and walk in robe, a sparkling central bathroom services the home perfectly.
The kitchen is truly the heart of the home, light filled and beautifully appointed with Caesarstone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, 900mm gas oven & cook top and dishwasher, large walk in pantry and an additional pantry to ensure there is ample storage space.
The well-defined open plan living design will ensure comfortability to all family members and guests. The two separate great sized living areas will be enjoyed by all, whilst a beautiful spacious decked alfresco makes for the perfect place to entertain guests all year round.
Set upon a generous allotment of approx. 400m2 with front and rear landscaped gardens, a double lock up garage, CCTV security system, LED downlights, ceiling fans and ducted heating throughout this home really does have it all.
The lucky new owner will move in with not a thing to do but enjoy the lifestyle on offer within one of Cranbourne East's finest estates. Surrounded by parks, playgrounds and Casey Fields sporting facilities making sure there will never be a dull moment in life.
Just a short drive to freeway access and all the amenities you will ever need including walking distance to the primary school scheduled to open in 2020. Additional schools nearby include Cranbourne Primary School, Cranbourne Secondary, Lighthouse Christian College, Saint Thomas Apostle Catholic Primary School and Marnebek School.

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you are looking to buy a house where you can simply move in, unpack and relax and is in walking distance to both Hunt Club Schools and a short distance to the Hunt Club village then 10 Monmouth Road needs to be seen to be appreciated!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 4 generous bedrooms plus an open study. The master offers a walk-in robe and full ensuite. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4, all with built in robes, are in close proximity to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with huge amounts of cupboard space and bench space, acrylic splash back, quality appliances including a cool touch glassed 600mm oven, gas burner hot plate, rangehood, dishwasher. All this overlooking the great sized family meals zone with sliding door access to the converted underroof alfresco that can be used as an added rumpus or sunroom.
Take advantage of the 2 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good book and a quiet glass of your finest wine in the front formal living area, that is segregated by a custom-made timber barn door. The carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the kitchen/meals family zone.
Added internal extras include downlights, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, multiple s/s air cons, ceiling fans and quality floor coverings and neutral colour tones throughout
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and a blank canvas for you to add your very own personal touch to front landscaping. A lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double lock up garage, that has internal access plus rear access to the backyard. For all those with extra cars, boats, caravans, work equipment the 2nd driveway with crossover and side gates for access to the rear yard surely must be a huge bonus. The outdoor living space is second to none, with a huge pitched roof decked pergola, with ziptrak café blinds that will make outdoor living a year-round feature. The kids and pets will have a blast with the great sized backyard with additional side veranda and garden shed.
The cheery on top of this already amazing house is the infinity gas hot water service and the 14 solar panels that will surely keep those ever-creeping electrical bills down to a minimum.
The Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Don't waste your time with a frustrating building process! It's all here waiting for you and you don't even need to lift a finger!

Description:
**SOLD BY PAUL RINGERI**
MAYFIELD ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST: Stylish from the footpath right through to the back fence, this is a home that would complement the lifestyle of a young family starting out and would sit perfectly in any investor's growing portfolio.
Set within an amenity filled location only minutes from the Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre, Casey Fields sporting precinct, Chisholm TAFE, Casey Grammar school and all of the facilities situated in the heart of Cranbourne, the home's position is undeniably good.
Fronted by an edgy contemporary facade 11 Symons Street is perfectly presented! Upon entry you are greeted by hard wearing timber look flooring, light paint tones and extras including LED lighting, high ceilings, ornate cornices and feature doors which all add to the overall appeal. Not forgetting the double glazing to all windows plus double tinting to selected rooms for added privacy!
From the entry hall you walk past the study, fitted with 2 built-in desks, and head towards the open plan living/dining area that incorporates the gorgeous hostess kitchen. Offering quality stainless steel appliances, mirrored glass splash back, stone bench tops and a walk-in pantry this has to be one of the main selling attractions. Not to mention the additional living area upstairs that can act as the ideal children's retreat!
Accommodation is in abundance as well with 4 genuine robed bedrooms upstairs including the master with a full ensuite that complements the family bathroom and bonus downstairs powder room.
Ducted reverse cycle heating and refrigerated cooling balance the climate year round, whilst outside you will be greeted by a remote double garage with internal access plus a North facing rear yard that has been carefully landscaped.
The location is A1 within moments to expansive parkland, a dog park, St. Thomas The Apostle primary school and local buses. Further afield you are also within a short drive to freeway access and all of the amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne.
With shopping precincts situated in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club, local amenities are always going to be close by. Don't forget about the proposed Cranbourne East train station and the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!

Description:
UNDER OFFER/ UNDER CONTRACT!
Proudly nestled in a quiet spot in The Avenues Estate is this magnificent fully appointed home!!
When open plan living is a must, look no further a spacious light -filled living/dining area situated in the heart of the home. The kitchen offers tiled splashback, dishwasher, 5 gas cooktop, overhead cabinets and more.
Take advantage of the 2 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie or a book with the front living area, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the family zone.
This delightful 4 bedroom home promises a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Grand master featuring a walk in robe and full ensuite. While remaining bedrooms offer built in robes. There is the bonus of a study which can be converted to a 5th bedroom.
Easy care front and rear gardens with plenty of room out back for kids and pets to enjoy or use it as a blank canvas for your next landscaping project.
Features include:
- Ducted heating
- Split system
- Close to all amenities
- Double lock up garage
Further afield you are also within a short drive to freeway access and all of the amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. The popular Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and the Casey Indoor Sports Centre are literally minutes away, whilst the shopping precincts situated in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club ensure that local amenities are always going to be close by. Cranbourne Botanical Gardens is only a short drive. Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station and the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.

Situated in the Livingstone estate sits this cosy family home complete with all the bells and whistles!
This open floor plan provides 3 generous bedrooms, the large master providing a full en-suite and walk in robe.

Description:
VERSATILE FAMILY LIVING
Conveniently located to everything with a large park and awesome playground just at the end of the street, this truly is the ultimate family home!
The large master bedroom (ensuite & WIR) is to the front off the widened hallway with a large multi-purpose room opposite (perhaps a 4th bedroom, home office or a 3rd living area - whatever you need it to be!).
The heart of the home is central & offers open galley style kitchen (with an amazing walk in pantry) which overlooks the casual living/meals area with the separate rumpus/theatre room off the dining. The remaining bedrooms & guest bathroom (separate toilet) are off the side hallway keeping it well zoned.
All of this on a fabulous 528m2 block with ample room for kids & pets! Further enhanced by a widened driveway & crossover to the remote double garage, security alarm, ducted heating, evaporative cooling plus split system for those humid summer days.
Even better this family home is perfectly positioned to every amenity you could need and has been freshly painted with brand new carpets & window furnishings. This property has not one cent left to spend! JUST MOVE IN, UNPACK AND ENJOY!
